{"tid":2488963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大灣區就業逾千空缺僅成功招聘25人","createTime":"2021-04-14T15:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:18:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d22fcc64c05aaa40e1de9e92e46688881704382","tid":2488963,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"本港失業率在武漢肺炎疫情打擊下攀升至7.2%，港府力谷年輕人「送中」工作，年初斥資逾4億元推出「大灣區青年就業計劃」，資助企業聘請本地的大學生。勞工及福利局局長羅致光早前稱，計劃已接獲逾5,000宗求職申請。但最新立法會文件中，勞工處指，截至今年2月28日，計劃秘書處只接獲25份企業成功招聘後所提交的津貼初步申請。文件顯示，招聘公司包括羅兵咸永道、騰訊、中國銀行等，但約8成職位月薪僅符合1.8萬元，即政府要求的薪酬最低門檻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/BCKG3YZVHZGEFHZSWQ6FUJMBNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FBCKG3YZVHZGEFHZSWQ6FUJMBNY%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=5367cf33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FBCKG3YZVHZGEFHZSWQ6FUJMBNY%2F&h=3c291e58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/BCKG3YZVHZGEFHZSWQ6FUJMBNY/</a>"},{"pid":"dec6bb1bc1ce1dec94ef34e99a69eb233e8bd332","tid":2488963,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"過幾年無政府資助唔知得返幾多呢"},{"pid":"ded221a7d7e1cd4e4a87f0113796591169ea3c79","tid":2488963,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"扣咗稅同 五險一金未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計埋好似over 30%"},{"pid":"c61046efc3cc561fd62fd84416d594c9c997606a","tid":2488963,"uid":156936,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"8成咁多阿<br />\n即係得20份夠18k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f2ac79dd2439b5d59ee45370998028169d6fd3","tid":2488963,"uid":309989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"香港讀完大學，返大陸食地溝油，